        {
            "id": 6244750,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 瀚宇博(5469)大漲7.01%，報93.1元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>瀚宇博(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5469:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5469\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5469-TW</a>)20日11:14股價上漲6.1元，報93.1元，漲幅7.01%，成交8,594張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>瀚宇博(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5469:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5469\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5469-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為電子零組件製造業。電子材料批發業。電子材料零售業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌5.23%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌4.89%，股價波動與大盤表現同步。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-1,702 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-4,223 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+2,687 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-166 張</li> <li>融資增減：-1,524 張</li> <li>融券增減：-118 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6244750",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 11:14:58",
